Class DocumentationRenderer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mmbase.framework.AbstractRenderer

          • org.mmbase.framework.DocumentationRenderer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Renderer

    public class DocumentationRenderer
extends CachedRenderer
    Currently renders documentation directly from subversion, using an XSLT to convert docbook to HTML. The idea is that a fall-back could be added to render the documentation from the xml's in a/the jar.

    MMBase-1.9.1
